import styled from '@emotion/styled'
import { AppBar, Avatar, Badge, Box, InputBase, Toolbar, Typography } from '@mui/material'
import React from 'react'
import MailIcon from '@mui/icons-material/Mail'
import NotificationsIcon from '@mui/icons-material/Notifications';
import SmsIcon from '@mui/icons-material/Sms';

const StyledToolBar = styled(Toolbar)({
  display: 'felx',
  justifyContent: 'space-between',
})

const Search = styled("div")(({ theme }) => ({
  backgroundColor: 'white',
  padding: '0 10px',
  borderRadius: '10px',
  width: '40%'
}))

const Icons = styled(Box)(({ theme }) => ({display: 'flex'
}))

const Navbar = () => {
  return (
    <AppBar position="sticky">
      <StyledToolBar>
        <Typography variant="h6" sx={{ display: { xs: 'none', sm: "block" } }}>Chatapp</Typography>
        <SmsIcon sx={{ display: { xs: 'block', sm: "none" } }} />
        <Search><InputBase placeholder='search...' /></Search>
        <Icons>
          <Badge badgeContent={4} color="success">
            <MailIcon />
          </Badge>
          <Badge badgeContent={4} color="success">
            <NotificationsIcon  />
          </Badge>
          <Avatar sx={{ width:30, height:30 }} src='https://scontent-vie1-1.xx.fbcdn.net/v/t31.18172-8/1147590_718281471515909_3805507_o.jpg?stp=cp0_dst-jpg_e15_q65_s320x320&_nc_cat=101&ccb=1-7&_nc_sid=e007fa&_nc_ohc=awwdpognY-8AX9camfP&_nc_ht=scontent-vie1-1.xx&oh=00_AfA_-n8-z9478LKxHGWenDQRfFk3YC6i6uTjxH6x1P5xjA&oe=639E474D'/>
        </Icons>
      </StyledToolBar>
    </AppBar>
  )
}

export default Navbar
